publisher			MumboJumbo							
publish_time	 2012年3月28日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Famed illusionist Harry Houdini knew he wouldn’t escape death forever.  When he promised his wife that he would try to reach her from the afterlife, it was seen as the ultimate stunt   But after years of séances, Bess was never able to reach Harry in this life or the next, and her spirit has come to you in a final plea to reunite her with her partner!Digging deeper into Houdini’s past, you’ll find bitter rivalries and interview Harry’s closest friends and his staunchest critics.  Consult famous friends like Sir Arthur Conan Doyle and rival Thurston the magician, while you solve puzzles and track Houdini’s ties to a super secret society.  Help Bess and Harry reconnect in Midnight Mysteries: Haunted Houdini!Key Features:Complete all-new adventure missions by solving puzzles, interviewing apparitions from the past, and searching for tools through beautifully locations that crisscross the globeIllustrated strategy guide to help you tackle puzzles and make connectionsIntriguing mystery story						
title	 Midnight Mysteries 4: Haunted Houdini			
